TITLE: Ready2Rumble Boxing DC.
SPEECH : N/A
RELEASE DATE : 13-07-2000

RELEASE NOTE:
In Ready 2 Rumble Boxing, players can compete as one of 16 boxers, each with their own fighting style. Each boxer is hyper realistic with an unlimited number of punch combinations for both realistic and over-the-top boxing styles. Manage fighting styles in "Championship Mode", train your boxers and save your head-to-head play. 